{"about_the_game":"Firefrost is a turn-based combat game about snow clearing. Use your flamethrower to burn through the snow, your enemies, and reach soup. Upgrade your flamethrower to unlock new tactical options. If you die, just get up again, no progress lost. Chase the SSoup rank, unlock more upgrades.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766260/extras/firefrost_thrower.gif?t=1708347233\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key features: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Flamethrower: the solution to the problem is always to burn the problem. The crux? You need your thrower to aim at the problem.<br></li><li>Make your own thrower: use upgrades for longer range, double shots (throws?) and exploding enemies to enable new tactical options. Put together your own combination of upgrades, and strive to find the perfect combination. <br></li><li>Chase ranks: learn enemy patters, plan your attacks and perfect your tactics. Become a tactical snow clearing elite and get that SSoup rank. <br></li><li>Modifiers: want a harder challenge? Use a modifier to limit your ammo or corrupt the world.<br></li><li>High quality sustenance: soup.</li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2766260?t=1708347233","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766260/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1708347233","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766260/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1708347233","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766260/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1708347233","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2769220,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"Firefrost is a turn-based combat game about snow clearing. Use your flamethrower to burn through the snow, yo